{"tid":271041,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果一個植物人 個思想係生活係佢幻想緊既世界","createTime":"2017-06-04T18:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T01:34:03.000Z","uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d77aef873e4d73e20740a660b67b55128a0c33b6","tid":271041,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:05:16.000Z","msg":"假設植物人係有思想，而佢個思想係生活係一個佢腦海中幻想出黎既世界<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，佢發緊一個好逼真既夢，佢係夢入邊有各項知覺，而且佢感受到時間流速同現實世界一樣，同時夢入邊既人都會同佢有交流<br />\n<br />\n如果係佢夢入邊佢係高富帥<br />\n<br />\n咁有兩個問題<br />\n<br />\n1。佢到底算唔算活着<br />\n<br />\n2。救醒佢，而佢係依個世界係窮撚，咁都底係咪害左佢？"},{"pid":"fbc2d39f1ced865599fe24d9a9a1104c570b8c6e","tid":271041,"uid":13667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:09:11.000Z","msg":"無限月讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24014a7458de3ab170b21ecbb713935a2a5f2c4","tid":271041,"uid":93287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:11:54.000Z","msg":"即刻諗起大雄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a467d7bf6acb82ddc5c499d8ef3992da11e3194","tid":271041,"uid":104513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:14:28.000Z","msg":"夢遺算唔算真係扑野？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8c856aec50cf94c92881670c8e8de992bc5226","tid":271041,"uid":64212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T23:43:35.000Z","msg":"你係唔係肯定自己唔係植物人？"},{"pid":"9284c34b1f16529c3345cf4aa7b26601af761331","tid":271041,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T23:56:10.000Z","msg":"植物人都活啦 題1無空間"},{"pid":"131544a31d5cc0ed42180df59c42c2560ef121f5","tid":271041,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T23:57:58.000Z","msg":"題2 係咪害佢要睇佢自己<br />\n不過魚蛋我一定唔會俾多佢"},{"pid"